messages.text: You got your wheels?
Where u wanna go?
Need a lift to hook up with Eva. Tomorrow night.
What happened to yours?
I'm grounded.
Seriously, my man? That's like a first.
What did you do, get a B in calculus?
Just pick me up after midnight - my block - at the corner.
Is this some illicit happenings?
Cause I got to get excitified about something.
We need to keep this on the low. I haven't seen her in weeks.
Our parents and this crazy weather are keeping us apart.
Like Ronan Farrow & Angelina Jolie?
you know - like in Shakespeare
Sure - just like them - only named Romeo & Juliet.
No worries, my man. Whatever you wanna call yourselves.
You can count on me.
the next night
been thinking abt what u said about fate
Yeah?
we don't know what will happen in the future -
so we use faith to deal with uncertainty
I see what you mean.
cause if we knew our fate -
we wouldn't need faith.
Do you have faith?
can't help but have it - it's how I was raised.
you?
I was raised to believe in evidence. But I was also taught to trust.
So I guess if you trust someone, you believe in them -
and even risk your life for them.
Maybe that's the kind of faith I have.
though it seems the universe is conspiring against us or testing us,
i have faith we'll be together again...soon.
Me too. I guess you really did convert me

a little bit later
Eva did you feel that?!
What?
The earthquake!
no! u ok?!
Another disaster. Riding with Jack and the ground began to shake -
Then a huge crater opens up in front of us!
We almost fell inside!!
where r u??!
Stuck on the beltway. No exit nearby.
Gotta go back. But cars starting to pile up. And too far to walk
shit the ground just moved here!
it's shaking like crazy!
stuff is flying off the walls -
Cover your head! Get under your desk!!
christ i'm scared!
Stay strong! I love you!
the next day
We'll try again.
Jack is going to pick you up first.
hope this works
Do you really believe in End Times?
after the past 2 nites i'm starting to believe it more
What does it mean?
it's like what we've been through but 1 million X worse
it's a global trial & judgement where the faithful rise 2 heaven -
but those who aren't will be left behind
You really believe that?
not really - i don't feel it inside.
but what about this weird weather? is it because of global warming?
Don't know. But there's alot of scientific evidence to support it.
what's gonna happen? will it get worse?
Drastic weather changes could displace the entire population -
and we'd be fighting infectious diseases, drought -
ending in eventual war and mass death.
what a future!
On the bright side sailing from the Atlantic to the Pacific will be much faster!
ðŸ˜†
Hang tight. We'll be together soon.
that's all i dream about...
that night
Jack's here - b with u soon!!
a little bit later
i don't believe it!
You caught in the storm?!
not just a storm - a big fucking hurricane!!
where r u?
in Jack's car - the wind tore off his side mirrors
u on the Beltway?
yes...shit - cars are blowing off the road -
can u drive to cover?!
Eva?
EVA?!!!
a little bit later
think we're safe now
WHERE?!
took a side road - broke into a hardware store
Are you hurt?
im ok - but Jack broke his arm slamming against the door
Stay inside. I'll find a way to get you both when the storm dies down.
u dont have 2 - Jack's dad is coming
Thank Jack and tell him I'm sorry.
he says u owe him a case of ðŸº
ðŸ‘
Will you be okay?
yeah - but we lost our driver
It was my fault for getting him involved in my stupid idea.
This was all wrong from the beginning.
what r u saying? u giving up?
No! Just maybe we should take a break. Till things cool down.
so ur quitting on us?
NO! But I think we should talk to our folks. Try to convince them to let us meet.
u lost faith in us
we don't need parents teachers or friends
all we need is each other.
is that something u can believe in?
You know it is.
then make a pledge
that u will let nothing get between us
I do.
and if something or someone does -
we get rid of them -
together.
To the death.
